                                      {
                                          "gid":  "1833968530900662",
                                          "title":  "A Bustling Frontier Benefits All Roles in Red Dead Online",
                                          "url":  "https://steamstore-a.akamaihd.net/news/externalpost/steam_community_announcements/1833968530900662",
                                          "is_external_url":  true,
                                          "author":  "rockstarintl_steam",
                                          "contents":  "The rising tide lifts all boats this month in Red Dead Online. Whatever your specialty, all Roles benefit from boosted bonuses. Bounty Hunters tracking targets, Traders wheeling and dealing in furs and pelts, and Collectors combing the frontier for treasure all stand to gain. \n\nAll the while, Naturalists can assist by sighting and sampling rare wildlife, and Moonshiners can get rich moving illicit swill right underneath the law’s nose. \n\nEarn bonuses and rewards across all Roles while taking advantage of waived Fast Travel fees, assembling a free Community-Inspired Outfit, and more through June 29.\n\n[img]{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/36260268/397d74ceed0ca674ed56d6f07a445be4f7a3f5c1.jpg[/img]\n\n2X RDO$ AND XP ON ALL BOUNTIES\n\nLicensed Bounty Hunters can dispense frontier justice and earn Double RDO$ and XP hauling in Regular, Infamous, and Legendary Bounties, dead or alive.\n\nComplete any Legendary Bounty through June 29 to get the Clovelly Shirt.\n\n2X RDO$ AND XP ON COLLECTOR SETS\n\nUnearth hidden valuables and sell Collector Sets to Madam Nazar to receive 2X RDO$ and XP in exchange. \n\nFind and collect a Fossil anytime this month to receive the Clovelly Dropped Suspenders.\n\n[url=https://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/39a3k38874o21a/a-bustling-frontier-benefits-all-roles-in-red-dead-online?utm_source=steam-news-rdr2\u0026utm_medium=o_promos\u0026utm_campaign=189\u0026utm_content=189-lead]See full event details at the Rockstar Newswire.[/url]",
                                          "feedlabel":  "Community Announcements",
                                          "date":  1780410594,
